    "Based on the needs of the use cases, developers and software architects choose which sort of blockchain system (private or public) and consensus method to utilize.",
    "Blockchain networks often use the Proof of Work (PoW) and Proof of Stake consensus techniques (PoS) [17].The original and most extensively used consensus mechanism is proof of work (PoW) shown in Fig. 6.",
    "Miners are faced with a mathematical challenge by PoW.",
    "The prize for solving the issue is a cryptocurrency given to the miner.",
    "The name of the award stems from the fact that it serves as evidence of the \"job\" completed."
  ]
